  <title>Rice cationic peroxidase accumulates in xylem vessels during incompatible interactions with Xanthomonas oryzae pv oryzae.</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=72e154a47bd9be12b005151a71a8df4e&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
